<dt>fredrik (Sep 27, 2002 3:15 am; Comment #4)</dt>
<dd>"A component could be implemented as a function or a class" tells us that a component can be implemented as a Python function or a Python class. Read the tutorial at <a href="http://www.python.org/doc/current/tut/tut.html">http://www.python.org/doc/current/tut/tut.html</a> if you don't know the difference.</dd>
